Like the previously seeded Norwich 1989 show, this has a rejigged info file and original (not extracted) shns converted to flac. This is a much rockier show - with Nik, and the second best drummer Hawkwind had during the 80&#039;s. Plus an exciting, lively audience sound, with an especially chainsaw-like Dave Brock guitar.

Hawkwind
Queensway Hall
Dunstable
U.K.
1983-02-10

Dave Brock: Guitar, keyboards, vocals
Harvey Bainbridge: Bass Guitar, keyboards, vocals
Huw Lloyd-Langton: Lead Guitar, vocals
Nik Turner: Saxophone, flute, vocals
Andy Anderson: Drums

This was Andy Anderson&#039;s 2nd gig (of only 8) with Hawkwind.
